  <div class="prose"><h2>Make.com Free vs Elevar vs Triple Whale vs Analyzify</h2><p>Server-side tracking is a solved problem. The question is whether you need to pay &pound;400&ndash;2,000/month for a managed solution or whether the free Make.com method gives you equivalent tracking quality. Here is the honest comparison.</p></div>
